latestReleaseNotes:
### Release info
Oobee is available as a desktop app for Mac and Windows. The setup files can be downloaded under `Assets` at the bottom of the page.

### Installation Guide
* Refer to the [Installation Guide](https://github.com/GovTechSG/oobee-desktop/blob/master/INSTALLATION.md) for Windows and Mac.

### What's New
#### Improvements
* Local file sitemap scan should have ability to set max pages by @younglim in https://github.com/GovTechSG/oobee-desktop/pull/170
* Spawn installer without powershell on Windows by @younglim in https://github.com/GovTechSG/oobee-desktop/pull/172
* Add Sitemap TXT support in docs and error message by @younglim in https://github.com/GovTechSG/oobee/pull/576
* Custom flow allow http and https only by @WilsonkwSheng in https://github.com/GovTechSG/oobee/pull/557

#### Bug Fixes
* Fixes Potential Electron high cpu usage on Tahoe macOS 26.0.1 by @younglim in https://github.com/GovTechSG/oobee-desktop/pull/173
* Fix missing Inno Setup ISCC binary in build step by @younglim in https://github.com/GovTechSG/oobee-desktop/pull/175
* Fix re-scan of same sitemap options causes invalid sitemap error by @younglim in https://github.com/GovTechSG/oobee-desktop/pull/176
* No pages scanned when scanning local file by @younglim in https://github.com/GovTechSG/oobee/pull/575

**Full Changelog**: https://github.com/GovTechSG/oobee-desktop/compare/0.10.68...0.10.70
